            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Kings.2:1-3:2",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Kings%202%3A1-3%3A2%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Final%20Instructions%20to%20Solomon%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20the%20time%20of%20King%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20death%20approached%2C%20he%20gave%20this%20charge%20to%20his%20son%20Solomon%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20going%20where%20everyone%20on%20earth%20must%20someday%20go.%20Take%20courage%20and%20be%20a%20man.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EObserve%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20and%20follow%20all%20his%20ways.%20Keep%20the%20decrees%2C%20commands%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20laws%20written%20in%20the%20Law%20of%20Moses%20so%20that%20you%20will%20be%20successful%20in%20all%20you%20do%20and%20wherever%20you%20go.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20do%20this%2C%20then%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20keep%20the%20promise%20he%20made%20to%20me.%20He%20told%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BIf%20your%20descendants%20live%20as%20they%20should%20and%20follow%20me%20faithfully%20with%20all%20their%20heart%20and%20soul%2C%20one%20of%20them%20will%20always%20sit%20on%20the%20throne%20of%20Israel.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20there%20is%20something%20else.%20You%20know%20what%20Joab%20son%20of%20Zeruiah%20did%20to%20me%20when%20he%20murdered%20my%20two%20army%20commanders%2C%20Abner%20son%20of%20Ner%20and%20Amasa%20son%20of%20Jether.%20He%20pretended%20that%20it%20was%20an%20act%20of%20war%2C%20but%20it%20was%20done%20in%20a%20time%20of%20peace%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A5a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EHe%20murdered%20them%20during%20a%20time%20of%20peace%20as%20revenge%20for%20deaths%20they%20had%20caused%20in%20time%20of%20war.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20staining%20his%20belt%20and%20sandals%20with%20innocent%20blood.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A5b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20some%20Greek%20and%20Old%20Latin%20manuscripts%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ewith%20the%20blood%20of%20war.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EDo%20with%20him%20what%20you%20think%20best%2C%20but%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20him%20grow%20old%20and%20go%20to%20his%20grave%20in%20peace.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Edon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20his%20white%20head%20go%20down%20to%20Sheol%20in%20peace.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBe%20kind%20to%20the%20sons%20of%20Barzillai%20of%20Gilead.%20Make%20them%20permanent%20guests%20at%20your%20table%2C%20for%20they%20took%20care%20of%20me%20when%20I%20fled%20from%20your%20brother%20Absalom.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20remember%20Shimei%20son%20of%20Gera%2C%20the%20man%20from%20Bahurim%20in%20Benjamin.%20He%20cursed%20me%20with%20a%20terrible%20curse%20as%20I%20was%20fleeing%20to%20Mahanaim.%20When%20he%20came%20down%20to%20meet%20me%20at%20the%20Jordan%20River%2C%20I%20swore%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20that%20I%20would%20not%20kill%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20that%20oath%20does%20not%20make%20him%20innocent.%20You%20are%20a%20wise%20man%2C%20and%20you%20will%20know%20how%20to%20arrange%20a%20bloody%20death%20for%20him.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ehow%20to%20bring%20his%20white%20head%20down%20to%20Sheol%20in%20blood.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20died%20and%20was%20buried%20with%20his%20ancestors%20in%20the%20City%20of%20David.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20had%20reigned%20over%20Israel%20for%20forty%20years%2C%20seven%20of%20them%20in%20Hebron%20and%20thirty-three%20in%20Jerusalem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20became%20king%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20throne%20of%20David%20his%20father%2C%20and%20his%20kingdom%20was%20firmly%20established.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESolomon%20Establishes%20His%20Rule%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20Adonijah%2C%20whose%20mother%20was%20Haggith%2C%20came%20to%20see%20Bathsheba%2C%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mother.%20%26%23x201C%3BHave%20you%20come%20with%20peaceful%20intentions%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BYes%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20come%20in%20peace.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20I%20have%20a%20favor%20to%20ask%20of%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20is%20it%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAs%20you%20know%2C%20the%20kingdom%20was%20rightfully%20mine%3B%20all%20Israel%20wanted%20me%20to%20be%20the%20next%20king.%20But%20the%20tables%20were%20turned%2C%20and%20the%20kingdom%20went%20to%20my%20brother%20instead%3B%20for%20that%20is%20the%20way%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20wanted%20it.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20now%20I%20have%20just%20one%20favor%20to%20ask%20of%20you.%20Please%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20turn%20me%20down.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20is%20it%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSpeak%20to%20King%20Solomon%20on%20my%20behalf%2C%20for%20I%20know%20he%20will%20do%20anything%20you%20request.%20Ask%20him%20to%20let%20me%20marry%20Abishag%2C%20the%20girl%20from%20Shunem.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAll%20right%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Bathsheba%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20speak%20to%20the%20king%20for%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Bathsheba%20went%20to%20King%20Solomon%20to%20speak%20on%20Adonijah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20behalf.%20The%20king%20rose%20from%20his%20throne%20to%20meet%20her%2C%20and%20he%20bowed%20down%20before%20her.%20When%20he%20sat%20down%20on%20his%20throne%20again%2C%20the%20king%20ordered%20that%20a%20throne%20be%20brought%20for%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20she%20sat%20at%20his%20right%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20one%20small%20request%20to%20make%20of%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20said.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20hope%20you%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20turn%20me%20down.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20is%20it%2C%20my%20mother%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20asked.%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20know%20I%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20refuse%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_21%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20let%20your%20brother%20Adonijah%20marry%20Abishag%2C%20the%20girl%20from%20Shunem%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_22%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHow%20can%20you%20possibly%20ask%20me%20to%20give%20Abishag%20to%20Adonijah%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20King%20Solomon%20demanded.%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20might%20as%20well%20ask%20me%20to%20give%20him%20the%20kingdom!%20You%20know%20that%20he%20is%20my%20older%20brother%2C%20and%20that%20he%20has%20Abiathar%20the%20priest%20and%20Joab%20son%20of%20Zeruiah%20on%20his%20side.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_23%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20King%20Solomon%20made%20a%20vow%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BMay%20God%20strike%20me%20and%20even%20kill%20me%20if%20Adonijah%20has%20not%20sealed%20his%20fate%20with%20this%20request.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_2_24%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20confirmed%20me%20and%20placed%20me%20on%20the%20throne%20of%20my%20father%2C%20David%3B%20he%20has%20established%20my%20dynasty%20as%20he%20promised.%20So%20as%20s